#: src/2857-roadmap-2020.md:25
msgid ""
"Every year, the Rust project plans out a roadmap, in accordance with [RFC "
"1728](https://rust-lang.github.io/rfcs/1728-north-star.html). The goal of "
"the roadmap is to"
msgstr ""

#: src/2857-roadmap-2020.md:28
msgid ""
"Align the Rust project on our priorities in the coming year, to help teams "
"focus their efforts on addressing the most prominent problems"
msgstr ""

#: src/2857-roadmap-2020.md:30
